            <h3>Introduction</h3>
            <p>Hello fellow SwoleCats! This page is for individuals
                who are just starting out in the gym (or possibly intermediate/advanced individuals)
                and are looking for a helpful guide on how to start actively living.
                This page will show you the basics on how to structure
